description: Disassociates a created artifact of an AWS resource with a migration task performed by a migration tool that was previously associated. This API has the following traits:

parameters.name: MigrationTaskName
parameters.description: Unique identifier that references the migration task to be disassociated with the artifact. Do not store personal data in this field.

parameters.name: CreatedArtifactName
parameters.description: An ARN of the AWS resource related to the migration (e.g., AMI, EC2 instance, RDS instance, etc.)
